        Constructor to all the additional data from a single game. Used in Analytical tools
        Parameters:
        damagedealt - Long format parameter for the dealt damage during the game
        damagetaken - Long format parameter for the taken damage during the game
        gamemode - String format parameter for the gamemode
        gold - Long format parameter for the earned gold in game
        duration - Long format parameter for the game duration
        date - String format parameter for the date when the game was played
        wardsScore - Long format parameter for the ward score during the game
        creepScore - Long format parameter for the creep score during the game
